  Text §I suspected as much, my friend, for your questions are most unusual. I must inform you that, a simple fisherman, I am a poor source of information about our local customs and such. I am sure there must be someone else who can tell you more. Why, I just know the right person. When you get to town, visit Bentic in the library in East Tenebrae. My good friend knows practically all there is to know about our land and its people. Yes, he can certainly help you.§
End

